{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a demo version of Tearscape, a 2D top-down action-adventure, blending fast-paced combat, exploration, and pixel art inspired by Game Boy Color classics. Fight monstrous foes, unlock new abilities, and explore a non-linear map filled with hidden secrets and dangerous challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, you will have access to the tutorial area, the graveyard, the forest, a small village, and the game's first dungeon, Dreadmoor Palace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/title_combat.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/combat.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master precise combat, where every strike and dodge matters. Strategically manage your stamina by carefully considering each move as you face off against grotesque enemies.\u00a0You have a limited number of healing flasks\u2014use them wisely and plan your moments to recover carefully. Upgrade your character's stats to remain effective and competitive in combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/title_items.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/items.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, discover the Shield hidden deep within Dreadmoor Palace, and use it to defend against more formidable enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/title_dungeons.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/dungeons.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, you will explore Dreadmoor Palace, the game's first dungeon, packed with deadly traps and challenging knight enemies. Awaiting you at the dungeon's end is the game's first boss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/title_bossfights.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/bossfights.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, face off against the game's first boss, Seraph the Impure\u2014a formidable adversary. With a combination of close and ranged attacks, Seraph will test your skills, but beware of the second phase, where unexpected and dangerous surprises await.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/title_exploration.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/exploration.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, you'll explore the game's opening areas: the graveyard, the forest, the abandoned village, and the first dungeon. The map is filled with branching paths and hidden shortcuts, so stay alert as you explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/title_npcs.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/npcs.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo introduces two NPCs: Valthor, who offers a small quest with a useful reward, and Aldric, your guide throughout the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736350067","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736350067","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/12a5ceaba5f5a41e43a2d3d5aaa2f9fa96df55d6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736350067","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/12a5ceaba5f5a41e43a2d3d5aaa2f9fa96df55d6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736350067","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a demo version of Tearscape, a 2D top-down action-adventure, blending fast-paced combat, exploration, and pixel art inspired by Game Boy Color classics. Fight monstrous foes, unlock new abilities, and explore a non-linear map filled with hidden secrets and dangerous challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, you will have access to the tutorial area, the graveyard, the forest, a small village, and the game's first dungeon, Dreadmoor Palace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steams