agraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/bossfights.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, face off against the game's first boss, Seraph the Impure\u2014a formidable adversary. With a combination of close and ranged attacks, Seraph will test your skills, but beware of the second phase, where unexpected and dangerous surprises await.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/title_exploration.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/exploration.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, you'll explore the game's opening areas: the graveyard, the forest, the abandoned village, and the first dungeon. The map is filled with branching paths and hidden shortcuts, so stay alert as you explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/title_npcs.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/extras/npcs.gif?t=1736350067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo introduces two NPCs: Valthor, who offers a small quest with a useful reward, and Aldric, your guide throughout the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["NERDS TAKE OVER"],"fullgame":{"appid":"3216340","name":"Tearscape"},"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271010/header.jpg?t=1736350067","is_free":true,"li